"spectrum" is a word that is used in many contexts.

In the context of autism, it means the range of abilities that an autistic person has.

In the context of light, it means the range of wavelengths of light that are visible to humans.

In the context of the human body, it means the range of temperatures that are comfortable to humans.

In the context of the human mind, it means the range of abilities that a human brain has.

